text:
Sylvia Goldscholl is 108 years old. Last month, she tested positive for #COVID19 and has beaten it. 

A tremendous life, a tremendous spirit, and a tremendous show of strength. So, to you, Sylvia, we send you all our best for many more years to come. https://t.co/Wds6NCc1qj
